      "chinese": "親屬站墳側兩排，由家屬最長者說最後的道別話：「一路走好，別再回頭！別驚嚇家人！」接著所有家屬跟著巫師走出來，巫師在門口處撒炭灰，每個親屬再次入室都需要跨越炭灰，並用桑葉來拍掃背部，表示除穢。拍掃完畢即展開家宴，巫師用的祭品或祭物，都歸屬於巫師的報酬。",
      "ab": "patavʉhlʉrʉ a cucusalia patʉkʉ vangʉhlarʉ maramasua,  hlamama saliana pilavalavaʉ maluliri “muavacavacangʉkia musala, tangumiacu’ai puaiaili pakikita hla kukia tahliaʉhlʉhlʉ cucusalia.” ruavicicu a marakʉmʉna cucusalia kipuhlu vahlita, muasiri a ʉlʉvʉna kitʉravahlita su’avu, angahlisana cucusalia musuarai ’avu’u puaruma, hla umaru rahlʉngʉ tahliusu aricacani marivautu likusu hlaka apuasala ’aʉrʉ, malilʉpʉngʉ, ruamiacu marisaiti kʉlʉsʉ, hliarumia pitamu avuraisa ʉlʉvʉna hlaka liuhluisa.",
